**EF Core and Central Package Management Demo**
#Description:
This project demonstrate how to use EntityFramework with Central Package Management (CPM) in a .NET console application.
It includes:

- SQL Server running in Docker container
- EF Core migrations and Bundle generation
  - Workflow:
  - dotnet ef migrations add InitialCreate
  - dotnet ef migrations bundle
  - ./efbundle.exe

- Design-time factory for CLI tooling

Program.cs - Configures DbContext using dependency Injection
MyContext.cs - Defines EFCore DbContext
MyContextFactory.cs - Enables EFCore  CLI tooling through design-time factory
Directory.Packages.props - centralizes NuGet package versions
efbundle.exe - Self-contained migration bundle executable

#Prerequisites:
- .NET SDK 6.0+
- Docker Desktop
- EF Core CLI tools: dotnet tool install --global dotnet-ef





